{"tid":493943,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗 : 我就是球壇歷史最佳 看不到有任何比我強的球員","createTime":"2017-12-09T05:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T11:23:00.000Z","uid":157545,"like":11,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d43bf14306741fdacc0e1f424fa2a5c8c8b24f7e","tid":493943,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/12/09/7/7c9e22d0711760e588a2d908cf106591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F7%2F7c9e22d0711760e588a2d908cf106591.jpg&h=9720bbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC.朗拿度昨天領取了自己的第5座金球獎，在接受採訪的時候C.朗拿度也認為自己就是球壇歷史最佳球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　前球員大衛-真路拿在金球獎頒獎典禮後對C.朗拿度進行了採訪，C.朗拿度說到：「我是球壇歷史最佳球員。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我看不到任何比我強的球員，沒有人能達到我的成就，我做到了其他人做不到的事。」<br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度還表示：「沒有任何一名球員比我更全面，我相信我就是歷史上最好的球員，無論是在高光的時刻還是低迷的時刻。」"},{"pid":"b63ba2a390566e7f784b08b7fde7479f29f187d2","tid":493943,"uid":9581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"Yes2.94%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abc7a3d0a806099239d42b9dfc7b3b49230f11d","tid":493943,"uid":17081,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/964/452/f20.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F964%2F452%2Ff20.gif&h=670ddc2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b592cd0f62cc5ef86c93bf72925e0cc3f4b6f828","tid":493943,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"9up"},{"pid":"734ed65f93074ad25dac739c1d2aa7804471c60f","tid":493943,"uid":152015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T06:25:2